═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
SIRAWAT COMMIT SIGNATURE POLICY v0.1
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

==CORE_RULE==
Commit không đúng Sirawat form không được nhận vào lineage.

Git có thể chứa commit kỹ thuật, nhưng Sirawat lineage chỉ công nhận commit có đủ form.
==END==

==REQUIRED_SUBJECT==
type(scope): message

Allowed type:
feat, fix, docs, chore, refactor, test, build, ci, perf, security,
audit, review, ratify, spec, doctrine, strategy, memory, proposal
==END==

==REQUIRED_BODY_FIELDS==
Sirawat-From:
Sirawat-To:
Scope:
Ground-Truth:
Decision:
Boundary:
Next-Signal:
==END==

==AUTHORITY==
Gatekeeper ratifies.
Thiên Lớn reviews.
Băng/Kim/Bối may propose, audit, flag, or prepare evidence.
No invented authority slot may ratify without Anh Natt/Gatekeeper.
==END==

==BOUNDARY==
Lifebook ANC Sirawat is not cookbook.
Sirawat entities are not recipe/material objects.
Private kernel/resolver/lineage authority remains inside Nhà.
==END==
